text: Lea Barta Yanitsas (born 15 March 1989) is an Australian water polo player. She played for the Australian women's national water polo team in the 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, 2017 World Aquatics Championships, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Australian water polo players
